Privacy policy
This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use the AI ARTY App. We are committed to safeguarding your privacy and ensuring the security of your data.
1. Data Collection
We want to assure you that our app does not collect, transfer, or store personal face data, including images or biometric information related to your face. We do not capture or retain any personal data related to your face during your usage of the app.
2. Information You Provide
When using the AI ARTY App, you may choose to upload images for artistic generation. These images are processed solely within the app and are not stored or used for any other purposes.
3. Usage Data
We may collect non-personal usage data, such as app usage statistics and technical information (e.g., device type, operating system), to improve the app's performance and user experience. This data is collected and used in an anonymized and aggregate form, and it cannot be used to personally identify you.
4. Cookies and Analytics
Our app may use cookies or similar technologies for analytical purposes. These cookies do not contain personally identifiable information and are used to enhance your experience within the app.
5. Third-Party Links
The AI ARTY App may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these external websites or services. Please review their respective privacy policies when accessing them through our app.
6. Security Measures
We employ industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. Despite our best efforts, please be aware that no online platform can guarantee absolute security.
7. Children's Privacy
The AI ARTY App is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe that we have inadvertently collected data from a child, please contact us to have it removed.
8. Changes to Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our data practices. Any modifications will be effective immediately upon posting. We encourage you to review this policy periodically for updates.
9. Contact Us
If you have questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or the AI ARTY App's data practices, please contact us at
https://www.ai-art-app.com
.
By using the AI ARTY App, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to this Privacy Policy.
Last updated: September 2023